turns.utterance: Hello, have you ever gone bowling before?
I like bowling every once in awhile, but I'm not very good. Do you know your best score for a round of bowling?
turns.response: If you get 12 strikes you can get a 300. Do you think you can ever get that?

turns.utterance: I don't think so, I don't have the dedication to get that good. Plus I'm always drinking when I bowl so that wouldn't help either, but that's what makes it fun.
turns.response: Maybe try bumper bowling. Have you ever gotten a Turkey which is three consecutive strikes

turns.utterance: Nope I don't think so. The real challenge for me is to not get a gutter ball, I'm happy with hitting any pins at all.
turns.response: So getting a hambone is way out of the question. It's four consecutive strikes.

turns.utterance: It is for me at least. Is there a special name for getting 5 consecutive strikes?
turns.response: Nope, very few people can do that. Do you play nine pin or ten pin?
